{"id":7785,"date":"2025-12-27T17:09:34","date_gmt":"2025-12-27T10:09:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=7785"},"modified":"2025-12-29T17:16:32","modified_gmt":"2025-12-29T10:16:32","slug":"gsc-thuong-hieu-noi-khong-voi-hang-kem-chat-luong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/gsc-thuong-hieu-noi-khong-voi-hang-kem-chat-luong\/","title":{"rendered":"GSC \u2013 Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2024 \u2013 2025, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u00ean t\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m gi\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng nh\u00e1i, h\u00e0ng l\u1eadu, kem tr\u1ed9n kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh ho\u1eb7c c\u1ed1 \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y trong quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, GSC gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1eddng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng: ch\u1ec9 cung c\u1ea5p s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m, c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c minh b\u1ea1ch, v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung k\u00eanh spa, th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n, clinic. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i b\u1ee9c tranh th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch GSC kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh cam k\u1ebft \u201cn\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"boi-canh-nam-2025-hang-gia-hang-lau-kem-tron-van-xuat-hien\"><\/span><b>B\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u0103m 2025: H\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng l\u1eadu, kem tr\u1ed9n v\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u0103m 2025, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ee3t ki\u1ec3m tra c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 quan ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng cho th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c v\u1eabn t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u n\u01a1i. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u00f3m s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u1ecb ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m g\u1eafn nh\u00e3n \u201cH\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\u201d, \u201cNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\u201d, \u201cch\u00e2u \u00c2u\u201d nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee9a corticoid v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u1ed9t t\u1ea9y<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kem tr\u1ed9n t\u1ef1 pha, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o l\u00e0 \u201ctr\u1eafng nhanh\u201d, \u201ctr\u1ecb n\u00e1m c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c\u201d.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m nh\u1eadp l\u1eadu, l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7786\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7786\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7786 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-1.webp\" alt=\"S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn tr\u00e0n lan\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-1.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-1-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-1-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-1-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7786\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn tr\u00e0n lan<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00e0: V\u00ec sao h\u00e0ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00fd do th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p l\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd chu\u1ed9ng gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb, th\u00edch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhanh. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ph\u00e1p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng \u201ctr\u00f4i n\u1ed5i\u201d. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c mua b\u00e1n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn khi\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 h\u01a1n, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng d\u1ec5 tin l\u1ea7m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>H\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m GSC c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, t\u1eadp trung cho spa v\u00e0 clinic<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng: x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u00e0nh cho k\u00eanh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, bao g\u1ed3m spa, th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 clinic. Thay v\u00ec ph\u1ee7 d\u00e0y tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00eanh b\u00e1n l\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea1i tr\u00e0, GSC t\u1eadp trung l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00f3 quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb da b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ee7 spa, ch\u1ee7 clinic t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1edbi m\u1edf \u0111\u1ebfn khi ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng. \u0110i\u1ec3m chung c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m an to\u00e0n, c\u00f3 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1y theo xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u201c\u0111\u1eb9p sau v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a GSC \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean nhu c\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf trong ph\u00f2ng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb: h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t n\u00e1m, m\u1ee5n, l\u00e3o h\u00f3a, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n, duy tr\u00ec h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng gi\u1eefa GSC v\u00e0 c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"san-pham-gsc-co-kiem-nghiem-giay-cong-bo-va-ho-so-phap-ly-minh-bach\"><\/span><b>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC c\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m, gi\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 ph\u00e1p l\u00fd minh b\u1ea1ch<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7787\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7787\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7787 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-2.webp\" alt=\"S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7787\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m GSC lu\u00f4n nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c l\u00e0 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 ph\u00e1p l\u00fd r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. M\u1ed7i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Phi\u1ebfu ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn phi\u1ebfu c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/span><\/li>\n<li>Xu\u1ea5t VAT v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi spa, th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c clinic, GSC cung c\u1ea5p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 ph\u00e1p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 l\u01b0u tr\u1eef. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap spa y\u00ean t\u00e2m trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng minh ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ranh gi\u1edbi r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 gi\u1eefa s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u00ednh th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng tr\u00f4i n\u1ed5i. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh b\u1ecf qua b\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e1p l\u00fd th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u khi b\u1ecb y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ki\u1ec3m tra.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nghien-cuu-va-san-xuat-tai-nha-may-han-quoc\"><\/span><b>Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7788\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7788\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7788 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-3.webp\" alt=\"S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7788\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y Enbioscience t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o m\u1ea3ng d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u, v\u1edbi quy tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Quy tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng d\u1eebng \u1edf vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t theo xu h\u01b0\u1edbng r\u1ed3i tung ra th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. M\u1ed7i c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3i qua c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc: ch\u1ecdn th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n, x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00ednh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1edd n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, n\u01a1i ng\u00e0nh d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh, GSC c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-noi-khong-voi-hang-kem-chat-luong-nguyen-tac-ro-rang\"><\/span><b>GSC n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ef1c tr\u1ea1ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch \u201c\u0111i t\u1eaft\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1ecb ph\u1ea7n nhanh, GSC gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft:<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng kinh doanh s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 ho\u1eb7c h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng tham gia v\u00e0o m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh h\u00e0ng x\u00e1ch tay, h\u00e0ng nh\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh ng\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh ph\u00e1 gi\u00e1, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c song song v\u1edbi GSC.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lu\u00f4n c\u00f4ng khai th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n tr\u00ean bao b\u00ec v\u00e0 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u1edf m\u1ee9c d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1eadp trung x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho spa v\u00e0 clinic, tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n h\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ee9c th\u1eddi.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng cu\u1ed1i, GSC cam k\u1ebft ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m qua k\u00eanh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u h\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3 ho\u1eb7c h\u00e0ng nh\u00e1i m\u1ea1o danh GSC, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u01a1 quan ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c x\u00e1c minh, x\u1eed l\u00fd.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-nhan-biet-san-pham-gsc-chinh-hang\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng nh\u00e1i ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tinh vi, vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1ec1 k\u00eanh ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p qua c\u1ea3 k\u00eanh ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kenh-chinh-hang\"><\/span><b>K\u00eanh ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng:<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7789\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7789\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7789 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-4.webp\" alt=\"Website ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a GSC\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7789\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Website ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a GSC<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>Website:<\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p>K\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb kh\u00e1ch l\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c spa\/clinic.<\/p>\n<p><b>Facebook:\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><strong>Cho spa\/clinic: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/gsc.globalshieldcosmetic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GSC &#8211; Global Shield Cosmetic<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>K\u00eanh chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u1ec1 da li\u1ec5u.<\/li>\n<li>Training online cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c: kinh doanh, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Cho kh\u00e1ch l\u1ebb: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/GlobalSkinCoaching\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GSC Cosmetic &#8211; D\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>K\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng tin chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC<\/li>\n<li>Chia s\u1ebb ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c ch\u0103m da chu\u1ea9n khoa h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><b>Shopee mall:\u00a0<\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/shopee.vn\/gsc.officialstore?page=0&amp;sortBy=pop&amp;tab=0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC.Official Store<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p>S\u00e0n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kenh-dai-ly\"><\/span><b>K\u00eanh \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd:<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7y quy\u1ec1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Spa, th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n, clinic c\u00f3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi GSC.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c k\u00eanh tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn thu\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n, tr\u00ean bao b\u00ec s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC s\u1ebd c\u00f3:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Logo GSC v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin tem ph\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, dung t\u00edch r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m mang t\u00ean GSC v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p so v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ni\u00eam y\u1ebft, ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u00f3a \u0111\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p l\u00fd n\u00e0o \u0111i k\u00e8m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi nghi ng\u1edd, ch\u1ee7 spa ho\u1eb7c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi GSC ho\u1eb7c nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eedi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh bao b\u00ec, tem, nh\u00e3n v\u00e0 h\u00f3a \u0111\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian nh\u01b0ng gi\u00fap tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ee7i ro cho c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng l\u1eabn \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb kinh doanh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-dong-hanh-cung-spa-va-clinic-trong-viec-lam-sach-thi-truong\"><\/span><b>GSC \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng spa v\u00e0 clinic trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng \u1edf vi\u1ec7c cung c\u1ea5p s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00f2n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o cho ch\u1ee7 spa, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt vi\u00ean v\u00e0 b\u00e1c s\u0129 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c, v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung xoay quanh:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 da v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t trong d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ph\u00e1p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 r\u1ee7i ro c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c d\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Song song \u0111\u00f3, GSC h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 spa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y gi\u00fap spa x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1eed t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi n\u00e2ng m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u1ee7a th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7790\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7790\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7790 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-5.webp\" alt=\"GSC cam k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-5.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-5-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-5-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/86-5-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7790\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GSC cam k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"noi-khong-voi-hang-kem-chat-luong-de-bao-ve-nghe-va-bao-ve-khach-hang\"><\/span><b>N\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ngh\u1ec1 v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn l\u1edbn, n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u00e0i ca \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c: t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c minh b\u1ea1ch, ph\u00e1p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi spa, th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 clinic. Vi\u1ec7c \u201cn\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi ch\u1ee7 spa, ch\u1ee7 clinic v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m an to\u00e0n, c\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd b\u1edbt h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb da c\u0169ng b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng h\u01a1n. Trong b\u1ee9c tranh \u0111\u00f3, GSC mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2024 \u2013 2025, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u00ean t\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m gi\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng nh\u00e1i, h\u00e0ng l\u1eadu, kem tr\u1ed9n kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh ho\u1eb7c c\u1ed1 \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y trong quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":7791,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16,13],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7785","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh","category-xu-huong"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7785","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7785"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7785\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":7928,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7785\/revisions\/7928"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7791"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7785"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7785"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=7785"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}